                <div class="comment-content">
        		<p>No doubt in my mind this article tops the list of all I&#8217;ve read in laying out most of this story&#8217;s highlights. Coming back for another look I was surprised there weren&#8217;t more comments, and felt guilty about not having offered my own kudos to Kimball on a job well done. I will definitely be posting this link around, and I have a feeling this article will get a lot of traction down the road.</p>
<p>Hopefully Kimball will at some point write more about the history of this epic cyber-saga. The way it went viral on the net, and the roles Bauer, Goodman and even quite a few significant skeptics have played in creating it&#8217;s legend. There are many stories within stories, and a cast of characters almost as hard to conceive as outrunning the wind that propels both Blackbird and the online discussion. Truly a blustery tale for our times.</p>
